image_analysis.description: This is a single page from a financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, filed by Donald J. Trump. The page is numbered 13 of 51 and details 'Part 1: Filer's Positions Held Outside United States Government'. It contains a table listing 15 organizations, along with the filer's position, location, and the dates the position was held. A footer provides explanatory notes.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header section with form information, filer's name, and part title. The main body is a table with seven columns. Below the table is a footer with two notes. A document identification number is stamped in the bottom right corner.
